Steps to run UVM:
1. source source_me 
	This will source the required modules and build the RTL and the TB
2. make sim_new
	This will run the simulations 


Steps to run formal verification for alu:
	cd formal_tb
        module load cadence/2016
        jaspergold formal_alu.tcl &

Steps to run formal verification for decoder:
	cd formal_tb
        module load cadence/2016
        jaspergold formal_decoder.tcl &
                
